---
const bgDarkBlue = "bg-[#2b3945]";
const textWhite = "text-white";
const borderGradient =
  "border-b-[10px] border-gradient-to-r from-[#6ee7b7] via-[#3b82f6] to-[#9333ea]";
{
  fontawesome: "css";
}
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
  <body
    class={`${bgDarkBlue} ${textWhite} flex flex-col justify-center min-h-screen`}
  >
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 px-4 md:px-6">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-left order-2 md:order-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl">
              Contacto
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
              ¿Tienes una pregunta o quieres trabajar juntos? Completa el
              formulario a continuación y nos pondremos en contacto contigo lo
              antes posible.
            </p>
          </div>
          <form class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <label for="name" class="font-medium"> Nombre </label>
                <input
                  id="name"
                  placeholder="Tu nombre"
                  class="focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary input-field"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <label for="email" class="font-medium">
                  Correo electrónico
                </label>
                <input
                  id="email"
                  type="email"
                  placeholder="Tu correo electrónico"
                  class="focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary input-field"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label for="message" class="font-medium"> Mensaje </label>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                placeholder="Tu mensaje"
                rows={5}
                class="focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary input-field"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="w-full rounded-md bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 sm:w-auto"
            >
              Enviar
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 order-1 md:order-1">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base">
            Nos pondremos en contacto contigo lo antes posible.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">+1 (555) 555-5555</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">info@acme.com</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-twitter"></i>
              <span class="sr-only">Twitter</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>
              <span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-instagram"></i>
              <span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .input-field {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 8px;
    border: 2px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .input-field:focus {
    border-color: #4f46e5; /* light blue focus */
  }
  .border-gradient-to-r {
    border-image: linear-gradient(to right, #6ee7b7, #3b82f6, #9333ea) 1;
  }
</style>
